public <K,​V> com.oracle.coherence.grpc.client.NamedCacheClient<K,​V> getNamedCache​(javax.enterprise.inject.spi.InjectionPoint injectionPoint)
        Produce a NamedCache gRPC client using the name from the @Name qualifier as the cache name and the name from the optional @Session qualifier to identify the gRPC Session to use to connect to the server.

        If no Scope qualifier is present the default gRPC session will be used.

        Type Parameters:
        K - the type of the cache keys
        V - the type of the cache values
        Parameters:
        injectionPoint - the injection point to inject the NamedCache into
        Returns:
        a NamedCache using the name from the Name qualifier as the cache name and the name from the optional Scope qualifier

        Produce a AsyncNamedCache gRPC client using the name from the @Name qualifier as the cache name and the name from the optional @Session qualifier to identify the gRPC Session to use to connect to the server.

        If no Scope qualifier is present the default gRPC channel will be used.
